{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Become <strong>Ghunter</strong>, a gnome chef that will create dishes by cooking creatures... <strong>ALIVE!!</strong> Use your various cooking based weapons to cook your prey alive and brutally finish them off with your multi-purpose melee weapon! Ghunter has the responsability to <strong>save the King</strong> by providing dishes to his servants and other characters to heal him.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><u><strong>FEATURES</strong></u><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156000/extras/COOKnHUNT.png.png?t=1736967989\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unlike other games, GHUNTER <strong>fuses</strong> the process of hunting and cooking in one. Use your multiple culinary-inspired equipment to create different delicious dishes!   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156000/extras/HuntNCookVideoGif.gif?t=1736967989\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156000/extras/InteractiveNarrative.png?t=1736967989\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game provides with an interesting and intricate narrative driven by charismatic characters with a dynamic narrative system where your dialogue choices matter. Unveil the mysteries of Gernik by finding lore inside the adventure. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156000/extras/InteractiveNarrativeGif.gif?t=1736967989\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156000/extras/GainUpgrades.png?t=1736967989\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">By finding different items in the adventure and completing customer orders, you will have the ability to upgrade Ghunter's equipment.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156000/extras/UpgradesVideoGif.gif?t=1736967989\" /> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">  <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156000/extras/ManageOrders.png?t=1736967989\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">GHUNTER's tavern is equipped with a order board where he will be able to pick up dishes to the player's choosing. Once completed, you will submit it to gain satisfaction of said customer.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156000/extras/ManageOrdersGif.gif?t=1736967989\" /> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156000/extras/CuteGore.png?t=1736967989\" /> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Despite looking so colourful and pretty, the world of Gernik is more unsettling than it meets the eye. Both the narrative and the cooking have a dark side.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156000/extras/PlentifulWorld.png?t=1736967989\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unveil the secrets of the world. Discover portals, landmarks, statues, chests and much more! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156000/extras/PlentifulWorldGif.gif?t=1736967989\" /> <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156000/extras/AdventureBook.png?t=1736967989\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Check all your progress and unlocks in the adventure book. Here you can see  the world map, lore entries, creature descriptions, recipes and more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156000/extras/LibroDeAventuraGif.gif?t=1736967989\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u><strong>More about this game</strong></u><br><br>Game developped as a  final project of the Art, Design and Programming masters of the U-tad university of Madrid, Spain. This project mixed all 3 of those departments with the help of other masters such as concept art, 3D modelers, animators and rigging.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156000/extras/17_UTAD_LOGO.png?t=1736967989\" /></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Champion Gnomechef","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3156000/e884123fa220ceb34208f775fea3db8bc4736e1a.jpg"},{"name":"Caldaria\u2019s Will","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3156000/a607a543e4c10fb01f786cae469ee08324efd639.jpg"},{"name":"Let him Cook!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3156000/1009b9db324e68d755a008f1581fbdb6f4ff38c1.jpg"},{"name":"Too Crispy","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3156000/c9843e307a428100c4dd9d414ca722553cf68078.jpg"},{"name":"Gastrognomical Strength","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3156000/ff84cfd1d629771480d58db39e34146d2ef553d0.jpg"},{"name":"Fondue Fanboy","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3156000/bc21baa7a547966cc6712b0dda326f20bcf69897.jpg"},{"name":"Michelin Star Gnomechef","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3156000/8a9d56772928e8f5ac510490557e4a674760f01d.jpg"},{"name":"Tourist","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3156000/7b6ec072fb35c72676181a9fcf8a7268639cece6.jpg"},{"name":"Aspiring Gnomechef!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3156000/aa11777ca428ff829310b400ed3d87e7ae900920.jpg"},{"name":"Glitchless Any%?","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3156000/a00578bf9d02706c6f57b7549c1ed803ad6aaba2.jpg"}],"total":28},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156000/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1736967989","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156000/page.bg.jpg?t=1736967989","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156000/501887e5168336df12bd8352f8b803bf380c667d/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1736967989","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156000/501887e5168336df12bd8352f8b803bf380c667d/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1736967989","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Partial Controller Support","id":18}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[2,5],"notes":"The game offers a gory combat when finishing off a creature."},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Become <strong>Ghunter</strong>, a gnome chef that will create dishes by cooking creatures... <strong>ALIVE!!</strong> Use your various cooking based weapons to cook your prey alive and brutally finish them off with your multi-purpose melee weapon! Ghunter has the responsability to <strong>save the King</strong> by providing dishes to his servants and other characters to heal him.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><u><strong>FEATURES</strong></u><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156000/extras/COOKnHUNT.png.png?t=1736967989\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unlike other games, GHUNTER <strong>fuses</strong> the process of hunting and cooking in one. Use your multiple culinary-inspired equipment to create different delicious dishes!   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156000/extras/HuntNCookVideoGif.gif?t=1736967989\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156000/extras/InteractiveNarrative.png?t=1736967989\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game provides with an interesting and intricate narrative driven by charismatic characters with a dynamic narrative system where your dialogue choices matter. Unveil the mysteries of Gernik by finding lore inside the adventure. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156000/extras/InteractiveNarrativeGif.gif?t=1736967989\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156000/extras/GainUpgrades.png?t=1736967989\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">By finding different items in the adventure and completing customer orders, you will have the ability to upgrade Ghunter's equipment.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156000/extras/UpgradesVideoGif.gif?t=1736967989\" /> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">  <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156000/extras/ManageOrders.png?t=1736967989\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">GHUNTER's tavern is equipped with a order board where he will be able to pick up dishes to the player's choosing. Once completed, you will submit it to gain satisfaction of said customer.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156000/extras/ManageOrdersGif.gif?t=1736967989\" /> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156000/extras/CuteGore.png?t=1736967989\" /> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Despite looking so colourful and pretty, the world of Gernik is more unsettling than it meets the eye. Both the narrative and the cooking have a dark side.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156000/extras/PlentifulWorld.png?t=1736967989\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unveil the secrets of the world. Discover portals, landmarks, statues, chests and much more! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156000/extras/PlentifulWorldGif.gif?t=1736967989\" /> <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156000/extras/AdventureBook.png?t=1736967989\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Check all your progress and unlocks in the adventure book. Here you can see  the world map, lore entries, creature descriptions, recipes and more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156000/extras/LibroDeAventuraGif.gif?t=1736967989\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u><strong>More about this game</strong></u><br><br>Game developped as a  final project of the Art, Design and Programming masters of the U-tad university of Madrid, Spain. This project mixed all 3 of those departments with the help of other masters such as concept art, 3D modelers, animators and rigging.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156000/extras/17_UTAD_LOGO.png?t=1736967989\" /></p>","developers":["Tiny Tavern"],"genres":[{"description":"Action","id":"1"},{"description":"Adventure","id":"25"},{"description":"Indie","i